On this week’s episode of portfolio watch we take a look at how share buy backs have shaped the performance of JSE listed companies, joined by Cobus Potgieter, Director, AIP Capital Management to understand what share buybacks can reveal about a company’s financial health and then speak to Thecla Mbongue, Senior Research Analyst at Ovum to examine the shift in mobile data pricing and what this means for profits in telecommunication sector.

